import React from 'react';
import { Container, Typography, Grid, Paper, Button, Box } from '@mui/material';
import { createTheme, ThemeProvider } from '@mui/material/styles';

const theme = createTheme({
  palette: {
    mode: 'dark',
    primary: {
      main: '#90caf9',
    },
    secondary: {
      main: '#f48fb1',
    },
    background: {
      default: '#1c1c1c',
      paper: '#2c2c2c',
    },
    text: {
      primary: '#ffffff',
    },
  },
});

function Showcase() {
  return (
    <ThemeProvider theme={theme}>
      <Container maxWidth="lg" style={{ marginTop: '20px', textAlign: 'center' }}>
        <Typography variant="h3" gutterBottom>
          How FlipVault Works
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
          Discover the benefits of using FlipVault.
        </Typography>
        <Grid container spacing={4}>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Paper style={{ padding: '20px', backgroundColor: '#2c2c2c' }}>
              <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom>
                Feature 1
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" gutterBottom>
                Description of how Feature 1 works and its benefits.
              </Typography>
              <Button variant="outlined" color="inherit">
                Learn More
              </Button>
            </Paper>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Paper style={{ padding: '20px', backgroundColor: '#2c2c2c' }}>
              <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom>
                Feature 2
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" gutterBottom>
                Description of how Feature 2 works and its benefits.
              </Typography>
              <Button variant="outlined" color="inherit">
                Learn More
              </Button>
            </Paper>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Paper style={{ padding: '20px', backgroundColor: '#2c2c2c' }}>
              <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom>
                Feature 3
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" gutterBottom>
                Description of how Feature 3 works and its benefits.
              </Typography>
              <Button variant="outlined" color="inherit">
                Learn More
              </Button>
            </Paper>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Container>
    </ThemeProvider>
  );
}

export default Showcase;
